lineage: Data is recorded on two public health systems.  The report is computer generated and manually manipulated to combine figures from both systems.  Figures are notifications given at the time and are categorised by possible/probable diagnosis given at the time and are subject to change on the receipt of formal diagnosis and receipt of lab reports.
